#: simsauth.module:1003
msgid "Allow Sync Password to LDAP Server."
msgstr "同步密碼到校務行政系統"

#: simsauth.module:1005
msgid "Check this box if you want to let people set passwords back to LDAP Server. Disabling this to prevent change password from the user profile form."
